      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRING ON BLING (2) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 30 from 59 starts. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when second (22.68) at Maitland. Solid record at the distance winning six races. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from six starts. Can go on with it. CYCLONE SEBAS (4) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (20.37) at Grafton behind Bing Bonus in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Expected to feature again. THAT'S MINE (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (22.78) last time in a NG at Gosford. Form here sound including eight wins. The form from his last run stacks up well. Cannot be taken lightly. FASCINATE GEORGE (3) will have admirers after placing last time out.",
